entry.string: The BBCode module allows you to use BBCode style mark-up in your content instead of, or with, HTML mark-up.
entry.translation: Zee BBCude-a mudoole-a elloos yuoo tu use-a BBCude-a style-a merk-up in yuoor cuntent insteed ooff, oor veet, HTML merk-up.

entry.string: The BBCode Module has no blocks included at this time.
entry.translation: Zee BBCude-a Mudoole-a hes nu blucks inclooded et thees teeme-a.

entry.string: The BBCode has transform hooks on the output, and form control hooks on the input to allow insertion of BBCode in content.
entry.translation: Zee BBCude-a hes trunsffurm huuks oon zee ooootpoot, und furm cuntrul huuks oon zee inpoot tu elloo insershun ooff BBCude-a in cuntent. Um de hur de hur de hur.

entry.string: Extended information about this module can be found here. [modules module]
entry.translation: Extended inffurmeshun ebuoot thees mudoole-a cun be-a fuoond here-a. [mudooles mudoole-a]
